casebody.head_matter:
ARKANSAS, et al., plaintiffs,
v.
DELAWARE.
No. 146 Original.
Supreme Court of the United States
Oct. 3, 2016.
Motion for leave to file Bill of Complaint and for leave to file Counterclaims is granted. The case is consolidated and the parties is allowed thirty days within which to file answers to the complaints and the counterclaims.
